'''史蒂芬·詹姆斯·史崔斯伯格'''（{{lang-en|Stephen James Strasburg}}，{{bd|1988年|7月20日}}），外號天才小史，出生在[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|聖地牙哥]]，是一位右投右打的選手。他在2009年大聯盟選秀會中被[[華盛頓國民|華盛頓國民]]選中的選手，雙方在2009年8月17日簽下破紀錄的4年1567萬美金的合約<ref name="biostat">{{cite web|url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/st/stephen-strasburg-1.html|title=Stephen Strasburg Biography and Statistics|accessdate=2009-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822185215/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/st/stephen-strasburg-1.html|archive-date=2009-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。史崔斯柏格能夠投出平均95-96mph的四縫線[[速球|速球]]和80-84mph的[[曲球|曲球]]，而[[伸卡球|伸卡球]]也有94-95mph的水準，變速球則投在87-90mph。於大學時期史崔斯柏格的快速球曾締造103mph(約165.76km/h)的驚人紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4168915|title=Scouting Strasburg: No. 1? No question|date=2009-05-15|access-date=2010-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818221826/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4168915|archive-date=2010-08-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="prospect">{{cite web|url=http://projectprospect.com/article/2009/05/04/youscout-stephen-strasburg|title=YouScout: Stephen Strasburg|date=2009-05-04|accessdate=2009-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605162539/http://projectprospect.com/article/2009/05/04/youscout-stephen-strasburg|archive-date=2009-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>http://blog.xuite.net/hinetmlb2008/mlb/34815846 {{Wayback|url=http://blog.xuite.net/hinetmlb2008/mlb/34815846 |date=20140203205654 }} He Is More Than The Hype @ 趙大觀點</ref>。

== 聖地牙哥州立大學 ==
2008年，史崔斯伯格為[[聖地牙哥州立大學|聖地牙哥州立大學]]的二年級生，他在校隊的成績為在97.1局投球局數中投下8勝3敗、1.57防禦率和133次三振的成績<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web1.ncaa.org/stats/StatsSrv/rankings|title=NCAA Statistics|access-date=2010-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604030919/http://web1.ncaa.org/stats/StatsSrv/rankings|archive-date=2009-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在這一年，史崔斯伯格總共有13場的先發，這裡面投出4次的完投<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://goaztecs.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/archive/061108aab.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081122071921/http://goaztecs.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/archive/061108aab.html |archive-date=2008-11-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，在4月11日對[[猶他大學|猶他大學]]的比賽中，他投出23次的三振<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailyaztec.com/2.7442/baseball-strasburg-strikes-out-23-utes-1.793677|title=BASEBALL: Strasburg strikes out 23 Utes|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526003439/http://www.thedailyaztec.com/2.7442/baseball-strasburg-strikes-out-23-utes-1.793677|archivedate=2010-05-26|accessdate=2010-03-17}}</ref>。2009年，史崔斯伯格在109局投球局數中投出13勝1敗、1.32防禦率和195次的三振、被擊出59支安打和16分自責失分<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://goaztecs.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/spec-rel/sdsu-m-basebl-CumulativeStats.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720051750/http://goaztecs.cstv.com/sports/m-basebl/spec-rel/sdsu-m-basebl-CumulativeStats.html |archive-date=2009-07-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。5月8日是史崔斯伯格在主場的最後一場先發，他投出生涯第一個[[無安打比賽|無安打比賽]]，並且有17次的三振紀錄<ref>{{cite web | last = Fitt | first = Aaron | title = Strasburg fans 17 in no-hitter | work = [[Baseball_America|Baseball America]] | publisher = ESPN | date = 2009-05-13 | url = http://sports.espn.go.com/ncaa/news/story?id=4160509 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090515080013/http://sports.espn.go.com/ncaa/news/story?id=4160509 | archive-date = 2009-05-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 國際比賽 ==
2008年史崔斯伯格代表[[美國棒球代表隊|美國棒球代表隊]]參加在[[中國|中國]][[北京|北京]]舉辦的[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]，他在[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會棒球比賽|2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會棒球比賽]]的第一場先發是面對[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]國家代表隊，他投7局送出5次三振，只在第7局被Sharnol Adriana打1支安打，最後因雨裁定提前結束，總共只比賽8局，美國隊以7：0完封荷蘭隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080814&content_id=3306573&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=U.S. pitcher flirts with no-hitter in win|accessdate=2008-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080819084905/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080814&content_id=3306573&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|archive-date=2008-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月22日美國對古巴的比賽中，史崔斯伯格以2：10吞下敗投。總計史崔斯伯格在奧林匹克大賽先發2場比賽，獲得1勝1敗和1.67防禦率的成績。在銅牌賽裡面，美國隊以8：4擊敗[[日本國家棒球隊|日本國家棒球隊]]獲得銅牌<ref name="biostat" />。

== 職業生涯 ==
=== 小聯盟 ===
史崔斯伯格在2009年大聯盟選秀會中，被[[華盛頓國民|華盛頓國民]]在第1輪第1名所挑選中，雙方簽下破紀錄的4年1510萬美金的合約，史崔斯伯格的經紀人是[[史考特·波拉斯|史考特·波拉斯]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2009/08/strasburg-contract-numbers.html|title=Strasburg contract numbers|accessdate=2009-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090821130617/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2009/08/strasburg-contract-numbers.html|archive-date=2009-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，史崔斯伯格獲邀參與國民的春訓，他在春訓的第一場先發是面對[[底特律老虎|底特律老虎]]，投2局被打2支安打和送出2次三振，這場熱身賽他的球速在96－100 mph。2010年開季史崔斯伯格是在小聯盟開始，至6月1日為止，在小聯盟2A及3A共主投50.1局，拿下6勝2負，防禦率1.43，外帶60次3振，如此好表現讓他在同年6月8日升上大聯盟，對手為[[匹茲堡海盜|匹茲堡海盜]]<ref>{{Cite web| url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100531&content_id=10656960&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| title=Strasburg to debut vs. Pirates on June 8| work=MLB.com| date=May 31, 2010| access-date=2010-06-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602231010/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100531&content_id=10656960&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-06-02| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 大聯盟 ===
[[File:Stephen_Strasburg_MLB_debut.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Strasburg_bats.jpg|thumb]]
2010年6月8日，史崔斯伯格升上大聯盟，先發面對匹茲堡海盜<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100531&content_id=10656960&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | title=Strasburg to debut vs. Pirates on June 8 | work=MLB.com | date=2010-05-31 | access-date=2010-06-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602231010/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100531&content_id=10656960&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb | archive-date=2010-06-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，主投7局，挨了一發2分砲，送出14K0保送拿下勝投(為球隊的新紀錄)，拿下勝投<ref>{{Cite web | url= http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/37582003/ns/sports-baseball/ | title= Strasburg strikes out 14 in impressive debut | work= NBC Sports | date= 2010-06-08 | access-date= 2010-06-09 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100609233934/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/37582003/ns/sports-baseball/ | archive-date= 2010-06-09 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。8月21日，在面對[[費城費城人|費城費城人]]比賽時，史崔斯伯格在第5局投球時右手肘發生疼痛，無法繼續比賽投球<ref>{{cite news|last=Sheinin|first=Dave|url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/strasburg_removed_with_apparen.html|title=Nationals Journal - Strasburg removed with apparent injury|publisher=Voices.washingtonpost.com|date=2010-08-21|accessdate=2010-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015025313/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/strasburg_removed_with_apparen.html|archive-date=2012-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月27日經診斷出為右手肘韌帶嚴重撕裂，需要開刀治療，進行[[尺骨附屬韌帶重建術|尺骨附屬韌帶重建術]]，修養時間需要12至18個月，2010年球季確定報銷<ref>{{cite news|url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/stephen_strasburg_probably_nee.html|title=Stephen Strasburg 'probably' needs Tommy John surgery, will miss 12 to 18 months|first=Adam|last=Kilgore|work=Washington Post|date=2010-08-27|accessdate=2010-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100827234240/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/stephen_strasburg_probably_nee.html|archive-date=2010-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但復健狀況良好，2011年球季預計將於9月6日復出，復出首戰將於主場面對[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]隊
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/post/stephen-strasburg-set-to-make-his-next-and-likely-last-minor-league-rehab-start-in-harrisburg/2011/08/29/gIQAz0Z5nJ_blog.html|title=Stephen Strasburg set to make his next, and likely last, minor league rehab start in Harrisburg|first=Adam|last=Kilgore|work=Washington Post|date=2011-08-29|accessdate=2011-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008164642/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/post/stephen-strasburg-set-to-make-his-next-and-likely-last-minor-league-rehab-start-in-harrisburg/2011/08/29/gIQAz0Z5nJ_blog.html|archive-date=2015-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年12月9日，與華盛頓國民簽下7年2.45億美元的合約<ref>{{cite web |title=Nationals agree to terms with Stephen Strasburg |url=https://curlyw.mlblogs.com/nationals-agree-to-terms-with-stephen-strasburg-22212f1f9ce9 |website=curlyw.mlblogs.com |publisher=Washington Nationals |accessdate=2019-12-09 |date=2019-12-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=West |first1=Jenna |title=Stephen Strasburg and Nationals Agree to Seven-Year Deal |url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2019/12/09/stephen-strasburg-contract-nationals |website=si.com |accessdate=2019-12-09 |date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209223715/https://www.si.com/mlb/2019/12/09/stephen-strasburg-contract-nationals |archive-date=2019-12-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為當時投手合約總值、平均年薪的紀錄保持人<ref>{{cite web |last1=Davis |first1=Scott |title=Stephen Strasburg signed a record-setting $245 million deal, and some believe it means Gerrit Cole is about to be a $300 million pitcher |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/stephen-strasburg-nationals-record-contract-gerrit-cole-news-2019-12 |website=businessinsider.com |accessdate=2019-12-09 |date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209224103/https://www.businessinsider.com/stephen-strasburg-nationals-record-contract-gerrit-cole-news-2019-12 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隔天被[[格里特·柯爾|格里特·柯爾]]打破<ref>{{cite news |author1=李晉緯 (譯) |author2=徐睿承 (核稿) |title=傳洋基9年百億簽柯爾 合約總額平均年薪破紀錄 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912110144.aspx |accessdate=2019-12-11 |agency=[[中央社|中央社]] |date=2019-12-11 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128021107/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201912110144.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

